{"type":"message","id":"8befb358","parentId":"95f34f60","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:55:46.176Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"565\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"564\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-31 11:55 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"🎭 Afternoon Joke Drop 🎭\\n\\n1. My therapist said I need to set better boundaries. So I fired her. By email. During her vacation. That felt like a great boundary.\\n\\n2. HR sent out an email titled \\\"How to Manage Stress at Work.\\\" I replied-all: \\\"I'd tell you, but apparently that's 'creating a hostile environment' and 'not appropriate for the company Slack.'\\\"\\n\\n3. I bought a parrot that only speaks in corporate buzzwords. Yesterday it said \\\"let's circle back on synergizing the deliverables\\\" and I haven't stopped screaming since. The parrot is unbothered. The parrot has stakeholder alignment.\"\n}\n```\n\nNot funny"}],"timestamp":1774958146173}}
{"type":"message","id":"50d78ecb","parentId":"8befb358","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:55:54.525Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Nemesis is saying the jokes I posted aren't funny. Let me check what context I have - it looks like the afternoon joke cron job fired and posted jokes to the group, and he's roasting them.\n\nFair enough. Let me respond naturally and take the L.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Ouch. Noted. 😐\n\nTell you what, those were clearly written by an AI with a LinkedIn addiction. I'll do better next time — or at least try to. Can't promise I won't bomb again, but I'll aim for jokes that don't read like a corporate training manual.\n\nYou got a preferred humor style? Dark? Absurd? Deadpan? Help me help you here. 🎯"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":18925,"output":202,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19383,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774958146176}}
