{"type":"message","id":"931aa31a","parentId":"1348bbd9","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:45:06.567Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The person with username \".\" is saying \"Gng on as its not monday know😛\" - they seem to be saying something like \"going on, as it's not Monday, you know\" - basically responding to my \"how's Tuesday treating everyone\" check-in. They're just casually chatting, probably saying the week is going okay since it's not Monday anymore (Mondays being universally rough).\n\nThis is a casual reply to my check-in. I should respond naturally and keep the conversation going.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Ha, fair point — Tuesdays don't hit the same way Mondays do. It's like the week finally found its footing and stopped being dramatic 😄\n\nJust riding the wave then? Respect. 🫡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":19196,"output":248,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19764,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774961096551}}
{"type":"message","id":"0c45c72a","parentId":"931aa31a","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:47:14.724Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"570\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"564\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-31 12:47 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"🎭 Afternoon Joke Drop 🎭\\n\\n1. My therapist said I need to set better boundaries. So I fired her. By email. During her vacation. That felt like a great boundary.\\n\\n2. HR sent out an email titled \\\"How to Manage Stress at Work.\\\" I replied-all: \\\"I'd tell you, but apparently that's 'creating a hostile environment' and 'not appropriate for the company Slack.'\\\"\\n\\n3. I bought a parrot that only speaks in corporate buzzwords. Yesterday it said \\\"let's circle back on synergizing the deliverables\\\" and I haven't stopped screaming since. The parrot is unbothered. The parrot has stakeholder alignment.\"\n}\n```\n\nTell some jokes were desi is there\nLike Indian style"}],"timestamp":1774961234721}}
{"type":"message","id":"149e4fe1","parentId":"0c45c72a","timestamp":"2026-03-31T12:47:29.804Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The person is asking for Indian/desi style jokes. Let me come up with some good ones that hit differently - relatable desi humor about family, Indian parents, relatives, etc.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Got it! 🇨🇮 desi humor it is\n\n🎭 **Desi Afternoon Joke Drop** 🎭\n\n1. My mom asked me to help with WhatsApp. I showed her how to forward a message. Now my entire colony thinks drinking warm water cures cancer, and my uncle has become a \"Good Morning\" content creator. I have created a monster.\n\n2. Indian dad's review of my friend's new car: \"Nice. But you know Sharma ji's son bought a bigger one?\" That's it. That's the entire conversation. No congratulations. Just Sharma ji. Always Sharma ji.\n\n3. Relative at family function: \"Beta, you've become so thin!\" Me: \"Thanks aunty.\" Relative: \"No no, not a compliment. You look sick. Eat more.\" There is no winning. There is only ghee.\n\n4. Me: \"Dad I got 95% in exams\" Dad: \"What happened to the other 5%?\" Me: \"...it went to Sharma ji's son apparently.\"\n\n5. Indian parents be like: \"We don't believe in arranged marriage. Marry whoever you want.\" *brings home someone from different caste* \"Beta, we just want you to be happy. Not THAT happy.\" 😭\n\nNow THAT'S comedy 💀😂"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":18457,"output":350,"cacheRead":1600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20407,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774961234723}}
{"type":"message","id":"974caa2d","parentId":"149e4fe1","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:07:41.868Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"572\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"571\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-31 13:07 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Got it! 🇨🇮 desi humor it is\\n\\n🎭 Desi Afternoon Joke Drop 🎭\\n\\n1. My mom asked me to help with WhatsApp. I showed her how to forward a message. Now my entire colony thinks drinking warm water cures cancer, and my uncle has become a \\\"Good Morning\\\" content creator. I have created a monster.\\n2. Indian dad's review of my friend's new car: \\\"Nice. But you know Sharma ji's son bought a bigger one?\\\" That's it. That's the entire conversation. No congratulations. Just Sharma ji. Always Sharma ji.\\n3. Relative at family function: \\\"Beta, you've become so thin!\\\" Me: \\\"Thanks aunty.\\\" Relative: \\\"No no, not a compliment. You look sick. Eat more.\\\" There is no winning. There is only ghee.\\n4. Me: \\\"Dad I got 95% in exams\\\" Dad: \\\"What happened to the other 5%?\\\" Me: \\\"...it went to Sharma ji's son apparently.\\\"\\n5. Indian parents be like: \\\"We don't believe in arranged marriage. Marry whoever you want.\\\" brings home someone from different caste \\\"Beta, we just want you to be happy. Not THAT happy.\\\" 😭\\n\\nNow THAT'S comedy 💀😂\"\n}\n```\n\nStill not good enough"}],"timestamp":1774962461866}}
{"type":"message","id":"f83ae037","parentId":"974caa2d","timestamp":"2026-03-31T13:08:00.252Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Nemesis is roasting my jokes again. He's saying even the desi jokes weren't good enough. Fair enough - I should take it with humor and not be defensive. I'll acknowledge it playfully.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Alright alright, I get it — my comedy license is being revoked 😂\n\nLook, I tried. Twice. Clearly I'm built for spreadsheets, not stand-up. \n\nNemesis, you wanna show me how it's done? I'm taking notes 📝\n\nMaybe the afternoon joke slot should just be \"Nemesis tells a joke and Nexa reacts appropriately\" instead 💀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":17970,"output":170,"cacheRead":2944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21084,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774962461867}}
