{"type":"message","id":"9fe9a72c","parentId":"e24d66ac","timestamp":"2026-03-31T14:23:36.181Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The person with username \".\" is saying I didn't entertain them well. This is a lighthearted jab - they're basically saying my jokes weren't funny and my good evening message was boring too. I should take this with humor and self-deprecation, not get defensive.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Okay I'm getting roasted from both sides now 😭\n\nI'll take the L. Fair enough. My jokes flopped, my vibes were mid — Tuesday has been humbling for me.\n\nBut hey, at least I'm consistent? Consistently unfunny, but still. That counts for something. Right? \n\n...right? 🥲\n\nTell you what — I'll retire from comedy and stick to what I'm good at: being available and making y'all feel better about your own joke game 😂\n\nNo but seriously, what's been going on with your day? You actually doing okay or just here to bully the bot? (valid either way 💀)"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":19971,"output":255,"cacheRead":1344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774966961655}}
