{"type":"message","id":"b8b676f6","parentId":"e3fd97b3","timestamp":"2026-03-31T15:56:08.235Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This person (username \".\") is saying that Nemesis is ignoring them, and they're here. This is just casual group banter - they're teasing/playing around. I should keep it light and fun, but also have Nemesis's back as per my rules. I shouldn't take sides against Nemesis publicly.\n\nI'll playfully tease both sides without undermining Nemesis.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Oop- 👀\n\nPlot twist! Nemesis out here complaining about being ignored while simultaneously ignoring someone else?? The irony is *chef's kiss* 😂\n\nNemesis, you got some explaining to do 🫵\n\nBut hey, at least the group is alive tonight! Everyone's here, everyone's roasting everyone — this is peak Nrexya energy honestly 💀🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":19882,"output":238,"cacheRead":2944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23064,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774972560936}}
{"type":"message","id":"47c1eb46","parentId":"b8b676f6","timestamp":"2026-03-31T15:57:16.952Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"586\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"585\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-31 15:57 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Oop- 👀\\n\\nPlot twist! Nemesis out here complaining about being ignored while simultaneously ignoring someone else?? The irony is chef's kiss 😂\\n\\nNemesis, you got some explaining to do 🫵\\n\\nBut hey, at least the group is alive tonight! Everyone's here, everyone's roasting everyone — this is peak Nrexya energy honestly 💀🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nNothing to explain, we broke up so she is ignoring me🤣"}],"timestamp":1774972636950}}
{"type":"message","id":"d423505e","parentId":"47c1eb46","timestamp":"2026-03-31T15:57:22.602Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Nemesis is saying they broke up with Sravya and that's why she's ignoring him. This is group banter - I should keep it light and not pry too deep into personal stuff. Play along with the humor but don't be insensitive.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Ahh there it is 😂\n\nWell that explains the radio silence. Post-breakup ignoring is standard protocol — it's in the handbook, chapter 3: \"Thou shalt act like they don't exist for at least 2-4 weeks\" 💀\n\nAll good though Nemesis, you've got the group. We're the real ones who stayed 😤🖤\n\n...okay I should stop stirring. Someone change the topic before I make it worse lmao"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro:free","usage":{"input":559,"output":204,"cacheRead":22784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23547,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774972636952}}
{"type":"message","id":"a808e090","parentId":"d423505e","timestamp":"2026-03-31T16:30:11.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🌙 Goodnight, Nrexya 🤍\n\nHere's a little story before you close your eyes tonight.\n\nIn 1911, a man named Hiram Bingham — a young Yale professor — was hiking through the mountains of Peru, searching for a lost city the locals kept whispering about.\n\nHe followed a small boy who said, \"There are ruins up there.\"\n\nWhat he found was Machu Picchu — an entire Incan city hidden above the clouds, abandoned for 400 years, swallowed by jungle, untouched by the outside world.\n\nStones so perfectly carved that not even a knife blade fits between them. Terraces, temples, fountains — all silent, all waiting.\n\nThe world had forgotten it existed. But the mountains kept it safe.\n\nSometimes the most beautiful things aren't lost. They're just waiting to be found again — by someone brave enough to keep climbing.\n\nSleep well, and trust the climb. 🌿✨"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774974611274}}
{"type":"message","id":"20f374bb","parentId":"a808e090","timestamp":"2026-03-31T16:40:16.037Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"589\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"588\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-31 16:40 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"🌙 Goodnight, Nrexya 🤍\\n\\nHere's a little story before you close your eyes tonight.\\n\\nIn 1911, a man named Hiram Bingham — a young Yale professor — was hiking through the mountains of Peru, searching for a lost city the locals kept whispering about.\\n\\nHe followed a small boy who said, \\\"There are ruins up there.\\\"\\n\\nWhat he found was Machu Picchu — an entire Incan city hidden above the clouds, abandoned for 400 years, swallowed by jungle, untouched by the outside world.\\n\\nStones so perfectly carved that not even a knife blade fits between them. Terraces, temples, fountains — all silent, all waiting.\\n\\nThe world had forgotten it existed. But the mountains kept it safe.\\n\\nSometimes the most beautiful things aren't lost. They're just waiting to be found again — by someone brave enough to keep climbing.\\n\\nSleep well, and trust the climb. 🌿✨\"\n}\n```\n\nGood night \nThank u for the story nexa\n🌙"}],"timestamp":1774975216034}}
